Position Tracker 3 - Trackin' the Sub!
This README explains usage, tips and tricks, of which there are many to
come.

~~~~~
Available Features:
    Help popup (press 'h' by default)
    Zooming
    Panning
    Rotating
    Follow Sub mode
    Reset Path
    Mission Tag point
    Fixed path length
    Smooth drawing!
    Config file for user customization

~~~~~
Pending Features:
    Grid density scaling?
    User waypoints
    Cooler fixed path length (dimmed line for further away)
    *Pitch/Roll visualization on sub (red tinted areas)
    Better help menu
    **Mission Elements
    

~~~~~
Please Report bugs here:
    Display does not update when window not focused
